<div class="container">
    <h1>Vegetarian Meal Plan</h1>

    <h2>General Guidelines</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Balanced Meals: Focus on a mix of protein, healthy fats, and carbohydrates.</li>
        <li>Hydration: Drink plenty of water throughout the day.</li>
        <li>Meal Timing: Aim for 3 main meals and 2-3 snacks daily.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Sample Meal Plan</h2>

    <h3>Breakfast</h3>
    <p>Overnight oats with almond milk, chia seeds, and topped with fresh fruit and nuts</p>

    <h3>Morning Snack</h3>
    <p>Hummus with carrot and cucumber sticks</p>

    <h3>Lunch</h3>
    <p>Chickpea salad with cucumbers, bell peppers, feta cheese, and olive oil dressing</p>
    <p>A slice of whole grain bread</p>

    <h3>Afternoon Snack</h3>
    <p>A small handful of mixed nuts and a piece of fruit (like an apple or banana)</p>

    <h3>Dinner</h3>
    <p>Stir-fried tofu with a mix of vegetables (bell peppers, broccoli, carrots) served over brown rice</p>

    <h3>Evening Snack (optional)</h3>
    <p>A small bowl of air-popped popcorn or a protein smoothie</p>
</div>

